{
  "stem": "21259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they go in the Yiddish stores, or the days when there's something, and they make-- they a few boys, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- then I was quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now like this, the Jewish afraid to go at night, even I was there, you know, to go in this section, the other section where they-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like-- like here is afraid to go in Harlem in night this time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, this time, like this was that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now very, very, very-- And-- and this I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, what I feel is, you know, what they do, what they do to the Jewish when Hitler was come, always, you know what they say before the war, Hitler is coming to you, and they kill you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this, by Polacks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was in 1938, when a lot of Germans, they run away from Germany, and they was coming to Poland, by [NON-ENGLISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this, of course antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is the reason in my heart, you know, I know they built special.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why-- now I-- I find out why they built the concentration camp always in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the concentration camp is in Poland, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Majdanek, Auschwitz, and-- in Lublin there is Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, the Polacks, when Hitler came in, then they killed all Jewish, a lot-- a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He got a store, a manufacturing store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They was working, you know, a Christian there was working, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After, when Hitler was coming, you know, they killed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got a beard, and they cut off the beard, and they took over the stores.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
